{"tid":492332,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"要追落後了　疑似 SONY Xperia 「全面屏」手機模型諜照曝光","createTime":"2017-12-07T12:10:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-08T11:29:30.000Z","uid":1130,"like":30,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"2facc6f9fbd0aa8c9be603a1a355359b8832e551","tid":492332,"uid":1130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T12:10:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.newmobilelife.com/2017/12/07/sony-xperia-full-screen-display-phone-leaked-photos/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newmobilelife.com%2F2017%2F12%2F07%2Fsony-xperia-full-screen-display-phone-leaked-photos%2F&d=JuSqV6q%2F1Y4mZ39y%2BfMHczOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=6a165cdd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.newmobilelife.com/2017/12/07/sony-xperia-full-screen-display-phone-leaked-photos/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/sony-xperia-full-screen-display-phone-leaked-photos_01.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.newmobilelife.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F12%2Fsony-xperia-full-screen-display-phone-leaked-photos_01.jpg&h=5b3896da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n主要手機廠之中，目前只有 SONY 的 Xperia 手機沒有無邊框「全面屏」設計，但在 2018 年，事情就有所改變了。<br />\n<br />\nMWC2018 會在 2018 年 2 月尾舉行，手機廠開始準備製作新手機，作為 Android 主要廠商的 SONY 也不例外。最近有來自高加索國家喬治亞的網站流出了疑似 SONY 新手機模型的諜照，諜照顯示了兩部完全不同的 Xperia 手機，其中一部呈矩形，帶有具有過去 SONY Xperia 外殼味道，但機背上方設有兩個偌大的鏡頭，另一部是像 iPhone 般的圓角矩形設計，機背中間有十足 Touch ID 的指紋認證，雙鏡頭設於機背左上角，而且是凸起的&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/sony-xperia-full-screen-display-phone-leaked-photos_02.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.newmobilelife.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F12%2Fsony-xperia-full-screen-display-phone-leaked-photos_02.jpg&h=d5b79139&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這兩款手機模型與過去 SONY Xperia 手機最大分別，就是機面螢幕採用了無邊框「全面屏」設計，其中一款更有 4K 解像度，以及嵌入螢幕的指紋識別。過去內置嵌入螢幕指紋識別的手機不多，2017 年中 VIVO 在推出了一款具備嵌入螢幕指紋識別的手機，成為一時佳話，相信明年初如果 SONY 在 MWC 2018 真的推出具備嵌入螢幕的指紋識別的 Xperia 手機，將會吸引不少目光。<br />\n<br />\n而規格方面，有關網站就指新 SONY Xperia「全面屏」手機會使用最新 Snapdragon 845 處理器，記憶體可能有 6GB，價格也許要 1000 美元以上。"},{"pid":"f9c1ab6e34d29fffd4b2457040a727829fb00ef2","tid":492332,"uid":1130,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T12:11:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/sony-xperia-full-screen-display-phone-leaked-photos_03.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.newmobilelife.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F12%2Fsony-xperia-full-screen-display-phone-leaked-photos_03.jpg&h=191d91a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/sony-xperia-full-screen-display-phone-leaked-photos_04.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.newmobilelife.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F12%2Fsony-xperia-full-screen-display-phone-leaked-photos_04.jpg&h=13d898be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/sony-xperia-full-screen-display-phone-leaked-photos_05.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.newmobilelife.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F12%2Fsony-xperia-full-screen-display-phone-leaked-photos_05.jpg&h=df729820&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/sony-xperia-full-screen-display-phone-leaked-photos_06.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.newmobilelife.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F12%2Fsony-xperia-full-screen-display-phone-leaked-photos_06.jpg&h=51fd9fc3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"24b7b70a1932e9b1f99d72e401601b9126976489","tid":492332,"uid":16061,"like":94,"dislike":101,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T12:12:55.000Z","msg":"幾靚都無用 行android"},{"pid":"e66a80915d9e36864442380e9eefb2f571adf9ce","tid":492332,"uid":