%3A%2F%2Fgss2.bdstatic.com%2F9fo3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy%2Fbaike%2Fw%253D400%2Fsign%3D8b0ca6f9898ba61edfeec92f713497cc%2Fdcc451da81cb39db8cc4c765db160924ab1830f8.jpg&h=1a925814&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67f4f39b40ba99d3c3958b4cad40b0be53c37fc6","tid":492332,"uid":49664,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T14:10:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://www.newmobilelife.com/2017/12/07/sony-xperia-full-screen-display-phone-leaked-photos/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newmobilelife.com%2F2017%2F12%2F07%2Fsony-xperia-full-screen-display-phone-leaked-photos%2F&d=JuSqV6q%2F1Y4mZ39y%2BfMHczOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=6a165cdd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.newmobilelife.com/2017/12/07/sony-xperia-full-screen-display-phone-leaked-photos/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/sony-xperia-full-screen-display-phone-leaked-photos_01.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.newmobilelife.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F12%2Fsony-xperia-full-screen-display-phone-leaked-photos_01.jpg&h=5b3896da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n主要手機廠之中，目前只有 SONY 的 Xperia 手機沒有無邊框「全面屏」設計，但在 2018 年，事情就有所改變了。<br />\n<br />\nMWC2018 會在 2018 年 2 月尾舉行，手機廠開始準備製作新手機，作為 Android 主要廠商的 SONY 也不例外。最近有來自高加索國家喬治亞的網站流出了疑似 SONY 新手機模型的諜照，諜照顯示了兩部完全不同的 Xperia 手機，其中一部呈矩形，帶有具有過去 SONY Xperia 外殼味道，但機背上方設有兩個偌大的鏡頭，另一部是像 iPhone 般的圓角矩形設計，機背中間有十足 Touch ID 的指紋認證，雙鏡頭設於機背左上角，而且是凸起的&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/sony-xperia-full-screen-display-phone-leaked-photos_02.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.newmobilelife.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F12%2Fsony-xperia-full-screen-display-phone-leaked-photos_02.jpg&h=d5b79139&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這兩款手機模型與過去 SONY Xperia 手機最大分別，就是機面螢幕採用了無邊框「全面屏」設計，其中一款更有 4K 解像度，以及嵌入螢幕的指紋識別。過去內置嵌入螢幕指紋識別的手機不多，2017 年中 VIVO 在推出了一款具備嵌入螢幕指紋識別的手機，成為一時佳話，相信明年初如果 SONY 在 MWC 2018 真的推出具備嵌入螢幕的指紋識別的 Xperia 手機，將會吸引不少目光。<br />\n<br />\n而規格方面，有關網站就指新 SONY Xperia「全面屏」手機會使用最新 Snapdragon 845 處理器，記憶體可能有 6GB，價格也許要 1000 美元以上。</blockquote><br />\n孖生兄弟左邊g pro   2    右邊同華為mate 10"},{"pid":"b5a655edbeb5b49a83b150694d96f3d75245a307","tid":492332,"uid":52276,"like":6,"dislike":4,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T14:12:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 要4K做乜？食撚曬啲電"},{"pid":"eb18f6f85b4bd25874b85c0e7bbf24e1a2918da9","tid":492332,"uid":5846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T14:32:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果可以行windows你話幾好..<br />\n一來無android咁多安全問題<br />\n二來又同iOS差唔多咁順<br />\n只係少啲app用</blockquote><br />\n少啲app用？直頭無app用呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18e1168c6b3012196bec80cefcfaca0a3d176c1f","tid":492332,"uid":69681,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T15:31:32.000Z","msg":"鏡面好型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f71c274ef5af5dc42e48151864a37dc8f508d9d2","tid":492332,"uid":1130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T15:32:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>鏡面好型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最後都係用case<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e93885216c780b46f66d33f8ef8463e9294c4124","tid":492332,"uid":30573,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T15:34:28.000Z","msg":"好撚假囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bb1ce0a7d1ac952324a1086ce523d96d614f8d4","tid":492332,"uid":51701,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T15:35:30.000Z","msg":"負皮係比8000 美元"},{"pid":"c8211ede34daffb7cabb4d5e438d8c16ce78fcec","tid":492332,"uid":69681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0